headline: Ameriprise Financial Celebrates 20th Anniversary as an Independent, Publicly Traded Company
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, October 09, 2025--Ameriprise Financial, Inc. (NYSE: AMP) debuted on the New York Stock Exchange in October of 2005 as the sixth largest spin-off in U.S. history—emerging as a new company and new brand with the distinction of being among the few firms in the U.S. with more than a century of corporate history.
